                <li>How you handled ambiguous requirements in an R&D project</li>
                <li>Collaboration with cross-functional teams</li>
                <li>A failed experiment and what you learned</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>Common Interview Questions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Explain the Scrum framework in your own words.</strong></li>
            <li><strong>How do you handle changing requirements mid-sprint?</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Describe a time you worked on a project with ambiguous goals.</strong></li>
            <li><strong>How do you prioritize when everything is "urgent"?</strong></li>
            <li><strong>What's your approach to estimating tasks?</strong></li>
            <li><strong>How do you handle disagreements with product owners?</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Describe your experience with remote/distributed teams.</strong></li>
            <li><strong>How do you stay productive with minimal supervision?</strong></li>
        </ol>

